text: Channing Matthew Tatum (born on April 26, 1980 in Cullman, Alabama) is an American movie producer and actor. He is a main actor in the movies Coach Carter, Dear John, Easy A, 21 Jump Street, its sequel 22 Jump Street, White House Down, The Lego Movie, Foxcatcher, The Hateful Eight, and in Hail, Caesar!. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Actors from Alabama Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:American dancers Category:American movie producers Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:People with dyslexia
